===============================
Parse or generate NDEF messages
===============================

.. image:: https://badge.fury.io/py/ndeflib.svg
   :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/ndeflib
   :alt: Python Package

.. image:: https://readthedocs.org/projects/ndeflib/badge/?version=stable
